                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18341124-165-offence-1 t18341124-cd-168"></join>6th of November</rs>, 2 shirts, value 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18341124-name-1216" type="victimName">
